    <h2 id="ï¸-project-of-the-day-internal-pki-quickstart-guide">ğŸ› ï¸ Project of the Day: â€œInternal PKI Quickstart Guideâ€</h2>
    <p><strong>Scenario:</strong><br />
Youâ€™re asked to create documentation to help an internal team spin up a basic private CA and issue test certs.
<strong>Steps:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>Generate a self-signed root CA cert</li>
      <li>Generate a subordinate cert (CSR â†’ signed by CA)</li>
      <li>Create an end-user or server cert</li>
      <li>Document trust path, install on server, and test with <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">curl</code> or browser
